PrecisOrder (a) approving an EXCHANGE OF LANDS between the NATIONAL CAPITAL COMMISSION and the PROVINCE OF QUEBEC whereby the NCC will acquire (and then convey them to the Department of Public Works and Government Services) three small pieces of land at the Canadian Museum of Civilization in Hull, and the Province will acquire some parts of the Autoroute 5 corridor, and (b) repealing Order in Council P.C. 1983-6/1519.
